# Web Admin UI

## Navigation
- Dashboard
- Catalog
  - Categories (tree editor)
  - Brands
  - Lines
  - Products (table + product card editor)
- Purchasing
  - Suppliers
  - Purchase invoices (draft/post/void)
- Stock
  - On-hand list
  - Movements history
  - Adjustments / Write-offs
- Reports
  - Summary
  - Category/Brand/Line
  - Top products
  - Stock alerts
- Settings
  - Costing method
  - Discount limits
  - Users & roles (Owner only)

## Product editor
- upload/set image
- assign category/brand/line
- default sell price
- barcode/SKU
- active flag
